# Cross-platform line endings. `text=auto` stores text files with LF in the repo (so a checkout on
# mac/linux is clean LF) while letting Windows keep its native CRLF in the working tree — and it
# prevents a contributor with autocrlf disabled from ever committing CRLF. Repo blobs are already LF;
# this just makes the contract explicit.
* text=auto

# Known binaries — never normalize or munge.
*.png  binary
*.pdf  binary
*.ico  binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
